                  </span></div><br><div class="comment">
                  <span class="c00">This sounds great, it&#x27;s been a long time coming and I&#x27;m sure many people will appreciate being able to debug their mingw generated executables in Visual Studio.<p>I did all of the PDB stuff in LLVM, happy to help if you need it (ping me on the mailing list or IRC)<span>
