                  <span class="c00">More precisely:<p>clang-cl is a drop-in replacement for cl (even the command lines are the same).<p>But clang-cl is just a driver for clang, and it&#x27;s still possible to get the ABI compatibility without clang-cl, but you have to know what you&#x27;re doing and get the flags right.<span>
