                  <span class="c00">I doubt this is very relevant in the case of Chrome compilers. It&#x27;s more about the huge investment&#x2F;expertise in Clang- or LLVM-based dynamic analysis and development tooling.<p>It&#x27;s just the better platform for writing these things. Heck, this is what is was built for in the first place. GCC is a solid, but also a very traditional compiler.<span>
